snippet.title: Divina catches Amber and Britney fighting | Nang Ngumiti Ang Langit (With Eng Subs)
snippet.description:
Divina (Pilar Pilapil) orders Britney (Heart Ramos) to stop communicating with Mikmik (Sophia Reola) after witnessing the child’s fight with Amber (Krystal Mejes). (With English Subtitles)
